  "IKMA執行役員・殿堂入": "IKMA executive officer / Hall of Fame",
  "WKF公認十段、本部派糸東流十段":
    "WKF-recognized 10th Dan; Motobu-ha Shito-ryu 10th Dan",
  清心流十段: "Seishin-ryu 10th Dan",
  イタリア侍道場館長: "Director of the Samurai Dojo, Italy",
  イスラエルクラヴマガチーフインストラクター:
    "Chief instructor, Israeli Krav Maga",
  世界武術師範協会会長: "President, World Martial Arts Masters Association",
  "清心流柔術九段、大東流八段、他":
